    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for model risk level 3. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged; the assessment team determined that the ASTM F1717 single-condition protocol is consistent with regulatory precedent and that the overall body of evidence is sufficient to support the intended decision. The FEA ensemble prediction is accepted as credible for the stated purpose.",
